@Request #30346:  Tools should not initially appear over the toolbar.

(Win32 only)
Test that any MLWorks tool windows do not initially appear over 
the toolbar.  They should also initially appear in a cascading 
fashion towards the bottom right of the screen.


---------------

Request #50056:  access to MLWorks windows via alt-tab.

(Win32 only)
Test that pressing alt-tab displays only one MLWorks icon and that
minimising or restoring MLWorks using the icon on the taskbar also
minimises or restores all other MLWorks windows as well.
@


